snippet.title: Project 5: Sightseer Gameplay
snippet.description:
20 minutes of roaming around while collecting minerals and salvage parts in.... Project 5: Sightseer.
Always playing/testing the latest games so If your new to the channel don't forget to 👊🏻 the like button and subscribe...👻

Open world multiplayer sandbox game. Explore the procedural world, discover resources and artifacts, build outposts, research technologies -- all together with your friends.

http://store.steampowered.com/app/655780/Project_5_Sightseer/

For more gaming, walkthroughs, tips and hilarious commentary subscribe to Heuster - https://www.youtube.com/c/HeusterHeu
